name: Heart of Azeroth

main_spell_tooltip.description:
Blast your target with a ball of concentrated flame, dealing 154 Fire damage to an enemy or healing an ally for 154, then burn the target for an additional 75% of the damage or healing done over 6 sec.

Each cast of Concentrated Flame deals 100% increased damage or healing. This bonus resets after every third cast.

passive_spell_tooltip.description: Your spells and abilities have a chance to cauterize your target for 498 Fire damage over 10 sec or to heal an ally for 498 over 10 sec.

Your damaging spells and abilities grant you 2 Haste for 4 sec, stacking up to 10 times. This Haste is lost if you stop using spells or abilities against the initial target.

When you have no stacks of Focused Energy, generate 5 stacks from your first damaging spell or ability.

Your spells and abilities have a chance to increase you and 2 other allies' Haste by 5 for 8 sec and reduce the cooldown of you and 2 other allies' currently slotted Major Essence by 1.0 sec.

Unique:  Corruption Resistance increased by 10.

Each time any ally within 40 yds uses an Azerite Essence, gain 6 Intellect and 3 Haste for 20 sec.

The ally who used an Azerite Essence also gains 3 Haste for 20 sec. Only one ally can have this Haste effect at a time.

Unique: Corruption Resistance increased by 10.

spells.description: Equip: Harnesses the energy of raw Azerite, awakening exceptional pieces of armor that possess latent powers.

description: A living symbol of hope, borne by the champions of a dying planet. The fate of Azeroth will be shared by all her children.
